# cg-probes .gitignore — BACKSTOP only. This release is built by allowlist, so the
# tree already contains only what should ship; this file just prevents accidents.

# secrets / env
.env
*.env
*.key
*.pem
*.7z

# python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# never (raw inputs / withheld data / internal scaffolding) — see README "What is withheld"
*ga4*
*employees*
iec-*
*site_search*
*unified_2025*
llm_responses/
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
memory/
*PLAN*
PAPER.md
REGISTRY.md
_archive/

# NOTE: the SHIPPED derived artifacts under */cache/ (probe datasets, golden set,
# headline embeddings, probe directions, result JSONs, figures) ARE committed on
# purpose — they are the reproducibility payload, not transient cache.